room_title: Escape room "The Great Pirate Escape" by Brainy Actz in Temecula
room_address: 28481 Rancho California Rd. Suite #108, Temecula CA, 92590
room_description: You are a group of intrepid explorers who, while on an expedition to discover an ancient buried treasure, were taken captive by a notorious Pirate from the seafaring days of yore. Can you escape his ship before he delivers you to Davy Jones in order to pay off a debt hundreds of years old? You will need to work together and use the clues at your disposal in order to escape!
